metadata.name: Loco
metadata.description:
Loco was a strange and imposing figure from the Crazy Mafia, a mysterious and feared organization, who had been summoned to the sinister world of CustomHorror. 
Not much is known about this world, but it is said to be a place of dark and unspeakable horrors, where only the bravest of souls venture and even fewer return. 
Loco and his allies fought a relentless battle against the chaos of CustomHorror, but it seemed that no matter how many of the vile creatures they dispatched, more would always take their place.
